high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up the green sponge on the counter.
Turn around and go to the pan on the counter.
Put the sponge on the pan on the counter.
Pick up the pan on the counter.
Turn around and go to the table by the window.
Put the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the pan from the counter to the table.

high_descs: Move to the right to face the counter top to the left of the sink.
Pick the green sponge up off of the counter.
Move to the left face the counter top and toaster.
Place the sponge on to the pan.
Pick up the pan from off of the counter.
Turn around, go to the left and face the end of the white table.
Place the pan with the sponge on top of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place the sponge that's in the pan on top of the white kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn left to face the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn around, move forward, turn right, then turn around again to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the sponge on the pan that is on the counter, in front of the toaster.
Pick up the pan with the sponge on it.
Turn right, go to the door, then turn right, then turn right at the table.
Place the pan on the table towards the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a sponge on it on the table.

high_descs: Step to the right to face the counter between the stove and sink.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the counter with a pan on it.
Place the sponge in the pan on the counter.
Pick up the pan with the sponge in it on the counter.
Turn right, walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room and turn right to face the end of the table.
Place the pan on the end of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge in a pan plus putting the pan on the end of a table.
